edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.gnsapp

Class VotesMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.gnsapp.VotesMap

  • public class VotesMap
extends Object
    A map between InetAddress OR InetSocketAddress and access counts. Note: This supports both InetAddress and InetSocketAddress as keys, but not in the same VotesMap.
    Author:
    westy
